399031.desc: All the preparations are now complete... Commander, let us sally forth and conquer these festival grounds! ...But before that, can we get something to eat first?
399031.name: Celebration Conquest!

999011.desc: Gascogne uniform change complete. Directive assigned: have fun on the beach with Master. Requesting detailed instructions for how to "have fun on the beach."
999011.name: Tropical Environs Acclimation Service Equipment

299021.desc: Hmph. One's outfit is merely superficial. True nobility must come from within. Don't you agree, Commander?
299021.name: White Warrick

10700030.desc: Hello, hello~! My name is Iori Minase! It's such a pleasure to meet you! ...Huh? There's no need for me to force myself...? Hey, wait a second, what do you mean by that?!
10700030.name: Iori Minase

299022.desc: So, an Eastern outfit this time... Hmph. My nobility is evident regardless of what I wear. However, since you prepared this outfit especially for me, it would be unbecoming of me to not express my gratitude. Thank you.
299022.name: Black Gerard

10700031.desc: Blowing bubbles while sitting on a swing... It might seem a bit childish, but there's nothing wrong with enjoying activities like these every so often.
10700031.name: A Little Evening Secret

10700070.desc: Nihihi~♪ I'm the idol, Mami Futami! You'll get to feast your eyes on how alluring Mami is, so look forward to it, Commander~!
10700070.name: Mami Futami

10700010.desc: Hello, Commander! I'm the idol, Haruka Amami! I'll do my best to share my dreams with everyone in port! Let's all have a great time together!
10700010.name: Haruka Amami

10700071.desc: Woah~! They're starting to send up the huge fireworks! ...Hey, Commander, just where are you looking? Did Mami's alluring yukata make you go crazy with desire~?
10700071.name: Alluring Festival

10700011.desc: Good evening, Commander! Are you also taking a break? If so, let's go get some candied apples and have a little chat~♪
10700011.name: A Taste of Tranquility

10700020.desc: Pleased to meet you. My name is Chihaya Kisaragi. Are you the one in charge of this port? I look forward to working with you.
10700020.name: Chihaya Kisaragi

10700021.desc: Oh, the fireworks display is starting. I'm planning to meet up with the others after this, but... Why don't we spend some time enjoying the view here first?
10700021.name: Reflections of Heavenly Flowers

10700060.desc: Nihihi! I'm the idol, Ami Futami! This place seems awfully lively, just perfect for pranking~! See you around, Commander!
10700060.name: Ami Futami

10700061.desc: Summer's all about the festivals, and Ami Futami's the queen of festivals! Even the fireworks soaring through the sky can't hold a candle to how brilliant Ami is, so keep your eyes on me, Commander~♪
10700061.name: Summer Flowers and Sizzling Beats

10500030.desc: G-Good Aquafternoon...! I'm Minato Aqua, the Gamer Maid from Hololive~ U-Ugh... I didn't know I would have to introduce myself in this outfit!
10500030.name: Minato Aqua

10500031.desc: Commander, good Aquafternoon~! Nice to meet you, it's Aqua, the Gamer Maid from Hololive! I'll show ya what the strongest maid can do!
10500031.name: Marine Maid

10500070.desc: Good Miovening! I'm Ookami Mio. Over here, I seem to be... some sort of aircraft carrier. Let's get along well.
10500070.name: Ookami Mio

10500040.desc: I'm the lovely high school girl affiliated with Hololive, Natsuiro Matsuri!! I love singing and having all kinds of lively conversations with people, so make sure to keep your eyes on me!
10500040.name: Natsuiro Matsuri

10500071.desc: I changed into my swimsuit, but I wonder if it looks right on me? An outfit like this might make you feel breezier just by looking at it~
10500071.name: Summer Vacation

10500041.desc: I'm the lovely high school girl, now in her extra-pure pajamas, Natsuiro Matsuri! Hey hey, Commander, what do you think? Surprised? Don't gawk at me too much~
10500041.name: Matsuri's Day Off

10500020.desc: Hey Commander, it's nice to meet you~! I'm Tokino Sora, a virtual idol affiliated with Hololive! I'll do my absolute best here like I always do! I'll be in your care, so cheer me on, Commander!
10500020.name: Tokino Sora

199021.desc: Oh? Commander, did you need to get some fresh air as well? Me? Ahaha... It's a bit too stiff inside that venue, so I came out for a change of pace. Why don't we take a little stroll together?
199021.name: South Town Pearl

10500021.desc: "Hello, my friends! I hope you're well~! This is Sora, on site at a beach in a slightly different world!" Beach visits just feel so invigorating, don't they? On another note, I can't swim…
10500021.name: Under the Clear Sky

399011.desc: Milord, it's starting to snow... If it suits you, please take shelter under Ibuki's umbrella.
399011.name: Winter Sylph's Reverie

10500060.desc: I am the mastermind magician, Murasaki Shion! Come and be bewitched by my mature, seductive outfit!
10500060.name: Murasaki Shion

10500061.desc: Here comes Murasaki Shion, Hololive's famous virtual magician! This world will bear witness to my brilliance!
10500061.name: Virtual Magician

399012.desc: This is my first time wearing Western clothes... Um, Milord! Does this outfit... suit Ibuki well...?
399012.name: Snow on the Wind

199022.desc: Heh heh, the warm sun and the sea breeze really hit the spot, don't they? Alright, let's get out there and enjoy ourselves! That's what you've been waiting for, right, Commander?
199022.name: Lanier Swan

299032.desc: I'll sing a song for you, Owner~ Ahem... Wait, I'm not sure I know any Dragon Empery songs, actually...
299032.name: Cait Sith Crooner

399013.desc: The Dragon Empery's "Spring Festival" is... filled with fun, liveliness, and pure jubilation. I can feel my true feelings welling up... Maybe, an environment like this would suit me pretty well...
399013.name: Arrival of Spring

199023.desc: Happy New Year, Commander! I guess you dress up all flashy like this for the Sakura New Year. Would you escort me...? What are you gawking like that for...? Haha, am I so dazzling? Hahaha!
199023.name: Exalted Vibrance

499028.desc: Ahh, the dreamlike beauty of this variation... let us write down this movement so that it may continue forever, my sweet child.
499028.name: Zeremonie of the Cradle

399048.desc: I must be dreaming, to be able to don this white veil... Haha, though, what's more important is our life together afterwards! Commander, please look forward to the rich fruit of my bridal training~
399048.name: Lily-White Longing

299011.desc: Hehe~ I usually let the other girls have all the glory, but even I must sometimes give you something to remember me by. Merry Christmas, Commander~
299011.name: Princess of the Reindeers

899021.desc: It is not against the teachings to halt one's pursuit of destiny and to surrender to the warm draft of festivities. It is mankind's prerogative to seek out auspicious portents.
899021.name: Lapis Lazuli's First Dream

10600030.desc: Are you the Owner of the port? The "Commander"? Hello. My name is Kasumi, I'll be staying here for the foreseeable future. I hope we can both get along on friendly terms.
10600030.name: Kasumi

399021.desc: You'd like to see my classical dance? Your tastes are quite refined, Commander... In that case, I'll show you the finest performance in the land!
399021.name: Izumo's Thousand Cherry Trees

10600031.desc: I was amazed to see the port had such a scenic place as this... Truly, you can't go without taking this view in. Right, Commander?
10600031.name: Springside Mist

299041.desc: Phew... Swimming like this doesn't feel all that refreshing... Hey, how about you stop staring and come join me?
299041.name: The Golden Hind's Respite

10600070.desc: Are you the one in charge here? The "Commander"? I'm Monica, the dealer! Well, dealer-in-training. I know it's sudden, but would you care to gamble with me? The stakes will, of course, be high!
10600070.name: Monica

10600010.desc: Hello! Oh... What am I supposed to call you? "Commander"? Got it! My name is Marie Rose. Just call me Marie, okay? I'm counting on your support, Commander!
10600010.name: Marie Rose

10600071.desc: "Welcome to Monica's Fantabulous Casino! Where you can have your every whim satisfied!" ...Oh, that doesn't sound very casino-managery? Heheh!
10600071.name: The Ace of Hearts

10600011.desc: Hmm, this swimsuit is pretty cute, but isn't it a bit childish? ...In any case, if you like it, then it's all good!
10600011.name: Devilish Servant Against the Splashing Waves

10600041.desc: A photoshoot? That'd be similar to what I did before coming here, but... um, this swimsuit is a bit much... Commander, is this what you're into? Geez... It's so embarrassing...
10600041.name: Golden Photoshoot

10600020.desc: Um... Are you the Commander? Oh, perfect! It's nice to meet you. My name is Honoka! I don't know how much I'll be able to help, but... let's be friends!
10600020.name: Honoka

10600021.desc: Whoa, the sea is so pretty~! It's as beautiful as the Venus Islands! I'm so blown away, I don't even feel the heat anymore!
10600021.name: Summer Angel on the Shore

299031.desc: Cheer up, Owner! Jeez, why are you so bummed out when we're at the beach... Because it's just a normal playdate instead of a romantic date? What's the difference anyway? C'mon, let's go head down to where the others are~!
299031.name: Summery Date!

499021.desc: I see, so this is a "kimono" from the Sakura Empire. Exquisitely crafted, comfortable to the touch, and elegantly designed... How to wear it? ...My child, what are you talking about?
499021.name: Dark Raiments of Gagaku

10600060.desc: Oh? You don't seem to fear me... Who might you be? ...I see, so it is you who rules over this place. Then I shall call you "Commander." I am Nyotengu. You would do best to keep me entertained, hehe.
10600060.name: Nyotengu

399041.desc: Commander? Oh, I haven't quite finished changing. My hair still needs work... Sorry, would you mind waiting a bit longer?
399041.name: Soft Voice of Spring

10600061.desc: Oho! To think there was a place with this much class... Not bad! I shall hereby be enjoying my hot springs vacation right here, hehehe.
10600061.name: Scarlet-Tinged Hot Spring Vacation

10600050.desc: Are you the person who led Misaki to this port? You go by the name... "Commander"? Hmm... I don't know how you sweet-talked her into it, but you're not fooling me. The moment you do anything strange... you better be on guard! My name? It's Nagisa. You... silly dog!
10600050.name: Nagisa

199013.desc: Supportive sorceress Seattle, comin' in hot! So, something got you down, my good pal? I'm up to talk about whatever's on your mind, but in return, you've gotta come to my party tonight!
199013.name: Sunfish Spell!

199012.desc: Meeeerry Christmas~! Even though the party is about to start, as you can see, I'm still getting ready~ Just gimme a moment, all righty~?
199012.name: Christmas Party Prep!

199011.desc: Hey! Great to have you here, Commander! I've gotta ask, whaddya think of my dress? Looking real gorgeous, right? ...Phew, awesome! I was worried my dress didn't look nice and might be dragging down the party mood, that's all!
199011.name: Gorgeous Party

899012.desc: Commander, regarding your next appointment... Ah, hard work is one of the highest virtues of the Iris's holy knights. On weekdays or vacations, in knights' armor or the Dragon Empery's attire, there can be no pause to my prayer, my training, or my duties as the administrator of your will.
899012.name: Alluring Administrator

899011.desc: With all due respect, Commander, this finery and this throne are not fit for one such as myself. Despite the hallowed name I have inherited, I am nothing more than a warrior. —However, if such an arrangement pleases you, then I shall hold my objections.
899011.name: Holy Knight's Resplendence

10700041.desc: Listening to the wind flow through the chimes on the porch seems to carry the summer heat right away. Commander, would you also like to come unwind with me?
10700041.name: Midsummer Relaxation

499041.desc: I thought I would never have time to pursue the fine arts, and yet here I am now. Your thoughts, Commander? Eastern as this calligraphy may be, does it not suit the connotations of my name?
499041.name: Black Strokes upon Blank Snow

10700051.desc: Sorry, what? A paddle showdown? Commander, please... You play that in a kimono, not a yutaka. But if you insist... If I win, you're buying me an ice cream!
10700051.name: Paddle Showdown - Summer Formation

10700050.desc: Pleased to meet you. My name is Ritsuko Akizuki. I was wondering what was going to happen to me when I suddenly got blown away, but... In any case, I'm pleased to make your acquaintance!
10700050.name: Ritsuko Akizuki

10700040.desc: Why hello, my name's Azusa Miura~ Um, this is a port, right? And these are... shipgirls? Um~ Where exactly am I?
10700040.name: Azusa Miura

10600051.desc: Whew! The wind feels great! ...What are you staring at me like that for, you silly dog? You're the one who said you wanted to go to the beach, remember? To start with, how about... we take a stroll?
10600051.name: Blue Skies, Good Vibes

499011.desc: Such a delightful party with our wonderful friends in this peaceful harbor... It's wonderful, really... But, it's all so boring...
499011.name: Dark Red Grin

10600040.desc: It's nice to meet you! From what I've heard, you're the "Commander," right? I'm Misaki. I have experience with various part-time jobs, so... I'm confident that I can be of help to you all. Let's do our best!
10600040.name: Misaki

10500051.desc: Be cheery, for here's Nakiri~! Ay am not used to this outfit and am a little embarrassed... But Ay am Nakiri Ayame, Hololive's virtual demon!
10500051.name: Summertime Nakiri

10500050.desc: Be cheery, for here's Nakiri! Ay am Nakiri Ayame, Hololive's virtual demon! Ay have come from the great beyond with my accompanying spirits!
10500050.name: Nakiri Ayame
